.TH DEVCLEAN 1 "July 2026" "devclean 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
devclean \- scan and clean developer cache directories
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B devclean
.RI [ command ] [ options ] [ targets ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
devclean scans common developer cache directories and can remove them safely. It supports cache analysis, recommendations, reports, and packaging-oriented workflows.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B scan
Scan known caches.
.TP
.B analyze
Analyze cache growth and provide recommendations.
.TP
.B clean
Delete selected caches.
.TP
.B stats
Show aggregate cache statistics.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --report markdown|html|csv|json
Emit a report in the requested format.
.TP
.B --dry-run
Show what would be removed without deleting anything.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
.B devclean scan --category python
Scan Python-related caches.
.TP
.B devclean analyze --report markdown
Generate a markdown analysis report with recommendations.
.TP
.B devclean clean --dry-run --exclude npm
Preview cleanup without deleting anything.
.TP
.B devclean analyze --category build --report json
Create a JSON analysis report for the build cache category.
